duties_responsibilities.duty: Provides direct social casework services to the participants of the Elderday Adult Day Health Care Program using person-centered care practices.
Performs social service support such as intakes, case management, assessment, and referral.
Participates actively in an interdisciplinary team environment.
Supervises social work assistants and social work interns.

education_certification.credential: Master's degree in Social Work (MSW) or related field (Preferred)
